WEBVTT

00:03.123 --> 00:06.421
How serious?
If the swelling gets worse, it could inhibit her breathing.

00:06.421 --> 00:09.780
I told you to notify me, if there was any trouble.
Now, you say this has been going on for days?

00:09.780 --> 00:12.493
Well, the monitoring equipment didn't detect
the symptoms until this morning.

00:12.493 --> 00:15.312
It isn't calibrated
for this type of patient.

00:18.923 --> 00:19.723
Well?

00:20.268 --> 00:23.118
The fever's diminished.
She's fighting it off.

00:23.165 --> 00:25.515
That's good news...
for both of you.

00:28.626 --> 00:33.576
Intravascular pressure has stabilized.
Blood oxygenation is good. She looks so innocent.

00:34.825 --> 00:37.925
It's almost possible to forget
what she represents.

00:40.429 --> 00:42.429
We don't want to disturb her.

00:44.829 --> 00:45.529
No.

